1	/**
2	 * Node chrome decorations — automates the outline-decorations spec
3	 * (openspec/changes/outline-decorations/specs/outline-decorations/spec.md).
4	 *
5	 * Every node kind gets the same tree-depth indentation and a consistent,
6	 * prominent marker (design.md D9/D10): headings/paragraphs/atoms get our
